# JonBeatz Image Workflow Rules

## Docs first

Before image/video tasks, read **`.cursor/docs/IMAGE-WORKFLOW.md`**. Model inventory: **`COMFYUI-MODELS.md`**. VRAM: **`VRAM-IMAGE.md`**.

## Environment

1. JonBeatz secrets live in **`D:\Hermes\projects\JonBeatz\.env.local`** — not MSC `.env.local` when working in this profile (run `npm run env:setup` to seed from MSC).
2. Personal outputs go to **`D:\Hermes\assets\media\{ProjectName}`** (JonBeatz: `D:\Hermes\assets\media\JonBeatz`) via `IMAGE_OUTPUT_DIR`.

## Hugging Face (cloud)

3. **`npm run image:gen -- "prompt"`** for quick txt2img — **zero local VRAM** (default free path).
4. Requires **`HF_TOKEN`** in `.env.local`. Run **`npm run image:doctor`** if missing.

## fal.ai (paid bonus — optional)

5. **`npm run image:fal -- "prompt"`** when Jon wants premium models or HF is capped — **pay-per-use** prepaid wallet.
6. Requires **`FAL_API_KEY`** in `.env.local`. Run **`npm run sync:mcp-env`** for Cursor **fal-ai** MCP.
7. Default model: **`FAL_IMAGE_MODEL=fal-ai/flux/schnell`** (~$0.003/image). See **IMAGE-WORKFLOW.md** for Nano Banana 2 / GPT Image 2 ids.
8. **Never replace** `image:gen` with fal for routine stills — fal is bonus only.

## ComfyUI (local GPU)

9. **Never start ComfyUI** unless Jon explicitly asks, runs **`npm run comfy:start`**, or sets **`JONBEATZ_COMFYUI_AUTO_START=1`**.
10. Before start, check **`npm run comfy:status`** or VRAM. Warn if **>65%** unless Jon uses `-NoVRAMCheck`.
11. Prefer **`npm run comfy:stop`** over full VRAM cleanup when only image VRAM should be freed (keeps LM Studio).
12. After local image/video work, **suggest `npm run comfy:stop`** to restore Mem0/LM Studio headroom.

## Workstation profile commands

13. Jon's PowerShell profile exposes **`gen-image-local`**, **`edit-image`**, **`inpaint-image`**, **`upscale-image`**, **`generate-video`**, **`animate-image`** — require ComfyUI on **:8188**.
14. Translate natural language to the right command; ask **cloud vs local vs fal bonus** when ambiguous.

## Boundaries

15. Do not apply MSC **deploy** or **Next.js** rules for image tasks in JonBeatz.
16. Log reusable prompts/styles to **Mem0** (`npm run mem0:add`).
